{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Group","title":"Group","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Classes","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"],"anchor":"Classes"},{"anchor":"Type-Aliases","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ColorOrangeBrandRawToken","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ColorOrangeDecorativeRawToken","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawToken"],"title":"Type Aliases"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Framework","symbolKind":"module","externalID":"OUDSThemesOrange","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"role":"collection","title":"OUDSThemesOrange"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This is the default theme any app should use, and can be subclassed to define for example themes dedicated to countries. The ","type":"text"},{"code":"InverseTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is based on it."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It embeds also in its target the brand colors which are not shared nor exposed in lower level targets or outside any module not depending to it."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In other words, this "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is based on the abstract "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", uses all the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" kit and brings the Orange brand colors and assets."}]},{"level":2,"text":"How to use the theme","type":"heading","anchor":"How-to-use-the-theme"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can use ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"text":" directly. To use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true},{"text":" without further modifications, you will have to use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":" for your root view and give it an instance of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep in mind the themes are "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift class objects","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and can be heavy, so you may use only as instance as singleton and not store any properties."}]},{"code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSThemeOrange \/\/ To get OrangeTheme","import SwiftUI","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, in your views, you can simply use the theme through an environment variable to get the tokens:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get the theme environment variable","import SwiftUI","","struct SomeView: View {","","    \/\/ Get OUDS environment variable for theme thanks to themeable view","    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme","    ","    var body: some View {","        ","        \/\/ Use the theme to retrieve the tokens","        \/\/ For spaces: theme.spaces","        \/\/ For sizes: theme.sizes","        \/\/ For borders: theme.borders","        \/\/ For elevations: theme.elevations","        \/\/ For opacities: theme.opacities","        \/\/ For colors: theme.colors","    }","}",""],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"How-to-enrich-the-theme","level":2,"text":"How to enrich the theme","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can enrich the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true},{"text":" by subclassing it or by overriding some tokens.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"text":"By subclassing","type":"heading","anchor":"By-subclassing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You may want to define your own theme, thus you can override the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" with your own class or just override the providers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will have to consider the tokens provider you need:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"spaces tokens are ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"sizes tokens are in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"colors tokens are all defined in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"borders tokens are in "},{"code":"OUDSBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"elevations tokens are in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"opacity tokens are in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"grid tokens are in ","type":"text"},{"code":"OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font tokens are in "},{"code":"OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ To use component tokens if needed","import OUDSTokensSemantic \/\/ To use semantic tokens if needed","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ To use raw tokens if needed","","\/\/ MAKR: - For semantic tokens","","\/\/ Token provider for spaces","","class YourAppThemeSpaceTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var spaceFixedMedium: SpaceSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension400","    }","    override var spaceScaledShort: MultipleSpaceSemanticTokens {","        MultipleSpaceSemanticTokens(compact: spaceFixedJumbo, regular: spaceFixedJumbo)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for sizes","","class YourAppThemeSizeTokensProvider: OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var sizeIconDecorative2xl: SizeSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension300","    }","    override var sizeIconDecorativeMd: SizeSemanticToken {","        DimensionRawTokens.dimension900","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for colors","","class YourAppThemeColorTokensProvider: OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var colorBgSecondary: MultipleColorSemanticTokens {","        MultipleColorSemanticTokens(light: ColorRawTokens.colorDecorativeAmber500, dark: OrangeBrandColorRawTokens.colorOrange900)","    }","    override var colorActionEnabled: MultipleColorSemanticTokens {","        MultipleColorSemanticTokens(light: ColorRawTokens.colorDecorativeShockingPink100, dark: ColorRawTokens.colorFunctionalScarlet600)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for border","","class YourAppThemeBorderTokensProvider: OUDSBorderSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var borderStyleDefault: BorderStyleSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderStyleDashed","    }","    override var borderWidthMedium: BorderWidthSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderWidth100","    }","    override var borderRadiusTall: BorderRadiusSemanticToken {","        BorderRawTokens.borderRadius800","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for elevation","","class YourAppThemeElevationTokensProvider: OrangeThemeElevationSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var elevationStickyEmphasized: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken {","        ElevationCompositeSemanticToken(ElevationRawTokens.elevationBottom_4_600)","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for opacity","","class YourAppThemeOpacityTokensProvider: OrangeThemeOpacitySemanticTokensProvider {","    override var opacityStrong: OpacitySemanticToken {","        OpacityRawTokens.opacity920","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for grid","","class YourAppThemeGridTokensProvider: OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var gridExtraCompactColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","    override var gridCompactColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","    override var gridRegularColumnGap: GridSemanticToken {","        GridRawTokens.gridColumnGap200","    }","}","","\/\/ Token provider for font","","class YourAppThemeFontTokensProvider: OrangeThemeFontSemanticTokensProvider {","    override var typeDisplayLarge: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens {","        MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(compact: FontRawTokens.typeRegular150, regular: FontRawTokens.typeRegular150)","    }","    override var typeCodeMedium: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens {","        MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(FontRawTokens.typeBold300)","    }","}","","\/\/ MARK: - And also for components tokens","","class YourAppThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider {","    override public var buttonSizeMaxHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","    override public var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.borderWidthThicker }","    override public var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.borderRadiusMedium }","    override public var buttonColorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    override public var buttonSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","}",""]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then define your own theme class and assign the providers:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To get OrangeTheme","","\/\/ Define your theme","class YourAppTheme: OrangeTheme {","    ","    override init() {","        super.init(colors: YourAppThemeColorTokensProvider(),","                   borders: YourAppThemeBorderTokensProvider(),","                   elevations: YourAppThemeElevationTokensProvider(),","                   fonts: YourAppThemeFontTokensProvider(),","                   grids: YourAppThemeGridTokensProvider(),","                   opacities: YourAppThemeOpacityTokensProvider(),","                   sizes: YourAppThemeSizeTokensProvider(),","                   spaces: YourAppThemeSpaceTokensProvider(),","                   button: YourAppThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then add the theme:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDS  \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To get OrangeTheme","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"By-overriding","type":"heading","text":"By overriding","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Quite simple and similar to the previous solution, but give only the provider to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For example for colors:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import OUDS \/\/ To get OUDSThemeableView","","@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: ","                OrangeTheme(colors: YourAppThemeColorTokensProvider(),","                            button: YourAppThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider())) {","                \/\/ Your root view","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"references":{"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangebrandfontrawtokens","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This enum helps to add new "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"font raw tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" exclusive to this "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such tokens are packed in a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift enum"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to gather them in one object with the suitable namespace and avoid to have just constants in nothing else"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(i.e. publicly accessible from everywhere). More optimized than 